songs.title: Can’t Fight Against the Youth
songs.album: Too Weird to Live, Too Rare to Die!
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Moving forward, using all my breath
"I'll make it up to you" is all I should have said
Mom and Dad, looked me right between the eyes
Then I awoke, a blinding light

[Chorus]
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)

[Verse 2]
In December, 1995
Though I had the thoughts, no one ever heard them right
Fought resistance nearly my entire life
Then I awoke, a blinding light

[Chorus]
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)

[Bridge]
Never going to take us, never going to break us
Future's open wide, and the past is all behind us
Never going to take us, never going to break us

[Chorus]
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)

Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
Woah-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
You'll never take us alive
Can't fight against the youth (Hey)
